opam-version: "2.0"
name: "ppx_base"
version: "v0.11.0"
synopsis: "Base set of ppx rewriters"
description: """
ppx_base is the set of ppx rewriters used for Base.

Note that Base doesn't need ppx to build, it is only used as a
verification tool."""
